          "settings": {
            "heading": "How many pockets do Workwear Originals Ultra women's scrubs have?",
            "content": "Pocket count varies by style. Tops are available in 2-pocket and 3-pocket options depending on the cut. Jogger pants are available with up to 5 pockets, while cargo and slim leg styles offer additional storage pockets. The zip front jacket includes 2 pockets. For the highest pocket count, look for the jogger styles — built to keep everything within reach through a full shift."
